  "texts": [
    "The density investigation started with an approximate estimate of the nuclei centers and measurement of their spatial locations.",
    "For that an Otsu threshold was used to filter the detected nuclei and reduce the amount of nonspecific signals resulting in a binarized image.",
    "The feature region of the nuclei in the binarized image were processed with morphological filters to remove small white noise and fill holes.",
    "For that we use morphological opening and closing.",
    "Regions near to the center of a feature region are defined as foreground and regions far away to a feature region are defined as background."
  ],
